INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 0, 0, 'Thank you all for attending this sermon. It\'s wonderful to see so many familiar faces!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34192, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 1, 0, 'Today I would like to touch on the three virtues of the Light.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34193, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 2, 0, 'These are dark and difficult times for us all. The armies of the Scourge amass to the south. Companions fall on the battlefield and rise to serve our enemy moments later.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34194, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 3, 0, 'Many of you have experienced a betrayal of trust.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34196, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 4, 0, 'Yet you persevere, as we all must. In these times, no one is a stranger to the virtue of tenacity. In the face of despair and hatred, we continue to stand true to our beliefs and fight on.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34197, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 5, 0, 'There can be no doubt as to your tenacity... but there are other virtues to consider.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34199, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 6, 0, 'Respect is the first virtue taught to those joining the path of the Light.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34200, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 7, 0, 'Look across the aisle to those you would call enemy. Despite the hatred that separates you, there are qualities to respect in your opponent. Their prowess should be acknowledged.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34201, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 8, 0, 'All of us gathered here have a concept of honorable combat. Conducting yourself with honor and treating your opponent as you wish to be treated shows respect.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34202, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 9, 0, 'Respect your opponent on the field, whether he be your brother or your sworn enemy. No matter where your beliefs truly lie, such respect is acknowledging a connection...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34203, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 10, 0, '...and in acknowledging those connections, you are closer to the Light.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34205, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 11, 0, 'There is one further step on the path of Light: compassion.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34206, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 12, 0, 'Rivalries abound in this day and age. It is easy to see differences wherever you turn.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34207, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 13, 0, 'The challenge is in looking beyond appearances and understanding our similarities. Through this understanding, you can feel compassion for the losses others have suffered...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34208, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 14, 0, '...even if the victim bears another banner.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34209, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 15, 0, 'By feeling and understanding compassion in enemy and ally alike, you reaffirm your connection with the world.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34210, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 16, 0, 'Acting on these tenets, these virtues, help make the world a place we all can appreciate. A world of honor and justice.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34211, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 17, 0, 'Think on my words, friends. In the darkness that surrounds us all, the Light is needed more than ever.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34212, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 18, 0, 'I\'ll be behind the confessional screen if anyone wishes to speak with me. Any doubts, any worries, any uncertainties I will happily soothe.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34216, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 19, 0, 'Take heart. Size isn\'t what matters, but how you use the skills you have.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34250, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 20, 0, 'What you lack in size you make up for in ambition and dedication, little one. Go with the Light.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34251, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 21, 0, 'Drink in moderation, then, my dwarven friend, but you may want to turn in your lance and reins for the time being. Go with the Light.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34259, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 22, 0, 'I understand your frustration. Your people are ferocious in battle, and this isn\'t what you\'re used to.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34285, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 23, 0, 'But this is a different sort of honorable combat. Difficult to adapt to, perhaps, but with your prowess I\'m sure you\'ll show everyone the strength in your people.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34286, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 24, 0, 'Besides... while an axe can be a valuable tool in war, lances have their uses as well.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34287, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 25, 0, 'It may seem pointless, but try to find pride in a good fight. The time will come when all this practicing and competition will be put to good use.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34292, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 26, 0, 'And your hair looks wonderful.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34293, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 27, 0, 'Your heart is in the right place, and I know you seek to serve the Light. But these small strikes do little to the great undead host.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34264, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 28, 0, 'This tournament is helping to form a strong, concerted force, though it may not appear obvious. When we\'re ready, the eyes of the Crusade and all its champions will turn towards Icecrown.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34265, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 29, 0, 'We will bring the might of all races to the Lich King, and he will be defeated.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34266, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 30, 0, 'I know this does not seem like the obvious path to you, but it will bring you closer to the Light. Fight well, brother.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34267, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (34102, 31, 0, 'Oh, my. Do you feel remorseful, at least?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34254, 0, 'Argent Confessor Paletress');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33462, 0, 0, 'I don\'t know if I can compete! Everyone is so much bigger!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34246, 0, 'Gnomeregan Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33462, 1, 0, 'I\'ve calculated the probability of my success, and it\'s distressingly low!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34247, 0, 'Gnomeregan Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33462, 2, 0, 'I can\'t accurately assess the mathematics behind the charge of my turbostrider while keeping hold of my lance at the precise angle needed and keeping my shield in the exact location for maximum protection at any given second!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34248, 0, 'Gnomeregan Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33462, 3, 0, '...and some of those mounts can trample me!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34249, 0, 'Gnomeregan Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33480, 0, 0, 'Lass, I\'ve a confession to make to ya.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34255, 0, 'Ironforge Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33480, 1, 0, 'I\'ve been feelin\'... urges.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34256, 0, 'Ironforge Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33480, 2, 0, 'It was a powerful feelin\' while I was listenin\' to yer sermon, and it\'s drivin\' me nuts!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34257, 0, 'Ironforge Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33480, 3, 0, '...I NEED A DRINK!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34258, 0, 'Ironforge Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33459, 0, 0, 'This isn\'t honorable combat. I long to face my opponents in battle with my axe in hand!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34269, 0, 'Orgrimmar Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33459, 1, 0, 'These are my enemies. YOU would be my enemy in battle! Your king has declared war on my kind!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34270, 0, 'Orgrimmar Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33459, 2, 0, 'But instead of fighting as my people would, as my people should, I find myself with a long, unwieldy pole, attempting to coax my wolf into charging my opponent without attacking.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34271, 0, 'Orgrimmar Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33459, 3, 0, 'This is not how orcs fight! My duty to the Warchief wars with my personal honor. I hold no faith in your Light, but as you seem an advisor, I would hear your words.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34272, 0, 'Orgrimmar Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33467, 0, 0, 'This fighting is endless. I\'m not certain how much more of it I can stand.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34289, 0, 'Silvermoon Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33467, 1, 0, 'All of this posturing, all of this dancing about in rings... it seems pointless. What\'s the use?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34290, 0, 'Silvermoon Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33467, 2, 0, 'And I\'m beginning to get HELMET HAIR. This is a travesty!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34291, 0, 'Silvermoon Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33477, 0, 0, 'My heart hangs heavier with each passing day, Confessor.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34260, 0, 'Stormwind Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33477, 1, 0, 'I have been ordered here, and here I stay and fight under the banner of Stormwind. But everything I do here is empty.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34261, 0, 'Stormwind Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33477, 2, 0, 'Beyond these reaches, the Scourge continue their work, destroying more and more of what we\'ve built. The fight should be there. I should be there.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34262, 0, 'Stormwind Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33477, 3, 0, 'How can I justify jousting while people die without my protection?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34263, 0, 'Stormwind Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33465, 0, 0, 'I punched a penguin on my way in here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34252, 0, 'Undercity Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (33465, 1, 0, 'Nah, not really. I just wanted to see the look on your face.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 34253, 0, 'Undercity Champion');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 0, 'My eyes! It burns... it burns...', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4438, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 1, 'Torture me no more! Release me, mortal! The Swamp of Sorrows... mortal... please...', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4439, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 2, 'Foolish mortal, I will rend your soul in two once I am released!', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4440, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 3, 'You are an agent of their wicked god, fool. I will see you destroyed!', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4441, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 4, 'My soul is not a trinket! Mortal, you must release me from these chains!', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4442, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 5, 'It hurts so much... Itharius, my old friend... Please help me...', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4443, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 6, 'Will the nightmare ever end?! I cannot force myself awake!', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4444, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` VALUES (8506, 0, 7, 'My charge to watch the temple has failed... my corrupted soul knows no peace...', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 4445, 0, 'Eranikus the Chained');
